256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 660, \"end\": 666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\", \"score\": 0.9999999689957808, \"rank\": 3.084743357249443e-08, \"text\": \"Moscow\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\"}, {\"begin\": 694, \"end\": 701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999999995243343, \"rank\": 4.710279699768642e-10, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China-Russian trade hit a record of $240.1 billion in 2023, up 26.3% from a year earlier, Chinese customs data shows.\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 821, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chinese shipments to Russia jumped 46.9% in 2023 while imports from Russia rose 13%.\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 822, \"end\": 829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999998907032992, \"rank\": 9.81772450214664e-08, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 843, \"end\": 849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999999851415852, \"rank\": 1.0318404923503424e-08, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 890, \"end\": 896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999999851415852, \"rank\": 1.0318404923503424e-08, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The world today is far from being calm.\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 948, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As member of the United Nations Security Council and as a responsible country, China urges with France for a\\u00a0truce\\u00a0in the world during the Paris Olympic games,\\\"\\u00a0Xi\\u00a0said, speaking through an interpreter alongside\\u00a0Macron\\u00a0during a joint statement.\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 1193, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations_Security_Council\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.362326459334697e-30, \"text\": \"United Nations Security Council\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations_Security_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations_Security_Council\"}, {\"begin\": 1028, \"end\": 1033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999939345636679, \"rank\": 5.7301124657835785e-06, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1045, \"end\": 1051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.9648095195301604, \"rank\": 0.03643425061292322, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 1161, \"end\": 1167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.68508683257437e-32, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Suspending armed conflicts under an \\\"Olympic\\u00a0truce\\\" is a longstanding tradition, and\\u00a0Macron\\u00a0has said he would work towards achieving one when Paris hosts the Summer Games from July 26 to Aug. 11 and the Paralympic Games until the end of August.\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1280, \"end\": 1286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.68508683257437e-32, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1337, \"end\": 1342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999740794, \"rank\": 2.6077911998546862e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French officials hope\\u00a0Xi's endorsement is a sign that he could use his influence to persuade Russia to reach a\\u00a0truce\\u00a0when President Vladimir Putin travels to China later this month.\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1622, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1441, \"end\": 1447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.9591728660272206, \"rank\": 0.042351236253001655, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 1534, \"end\": 1540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999999851415852, \"rank\": 1.0318404923503424e-08, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 1573, \"end\": 1587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4682831456396872e-28, \"text\": \"Vladimir Putin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\"}, {\"begin\": 1599, \"end\": 1604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999939345636679, \"rank\": 5.7301124657835785e-06, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their hope is that a small\\u00a0truce\\u00a0could open the window to broader diplomacy.\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1700, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We wanted to explain the impact of this conflict on Europe's security and our determination to support Ukraine for as long as necessary,\\\"\\u00a0Macron\\u00a0said, adding that Paris was not looking to change the regime in Moscow.\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1806, \"end\": 1813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999999995243343, \"rank\": 4.710279699768642e-10, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 1841, \"end\": 1847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.68508683257437e-32, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1866, \"end\": 1871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999740794, \"rank\": 2.6077911998546862e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1912, \"end\": 1918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\", \"score\": 0.9999999689957808, \"rank\": 3.084743357249443e-08, \"text\": \"Moscow\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Macron\\u00a0said he hoped Putin's visit to China would help assess the perspectives for peace.\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 2010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1921, \"end\": 1927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.68508683257437e-32, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1942, \"end\": 1947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5230187515084826e-38, \"text\": \"Putin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\"}, {\"begin\": 1959, \"end\": 1964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999939345636679, \"rank\": 5.7301124657835785e-06, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Xi\\u00a0said he supported an international peace conference supported by Russia and Ukraine, appearing to be lukewarm on a peace conference organized by Switzerland on June 16, to which Moscow has not been invited.\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2080, \"end\": 2086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999999851415852, \"rank\": 1.0318404923503424e-08, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 2091, \"end\": 2098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999999995243343, \"rank\": 4.710279699768642e-10, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 2160, \"end\": 2171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9999999854326235, \"rank\": 1.4549840511660368e-08, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}, {\"begin\": 2193, \"end\": 2199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\", \"score\": 0.9999999689957808, \"rank\": 3.084743357249443e-08, \"text\": \"Moscow\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are opposed to using this crisis to place the responsibilities on a third country and tarnish its image and incite a new Cold War,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2367, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"History has shown conflicts can only be resolved by negotiations.\\\"\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2436, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fighting on Ukraine's eastern front has worsened in recent weeks as Kyiv's troops await crucial U.S. and European military aid to beat back a Russian advance.\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2450, \"end\": 2457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999999995243343, \"rank\": 4.710279699768642e-10, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 2506, \"end\": 2510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyiv\", \"score\": 0.9999999998412932, \"rank\": 1.588649609736223e-10, \"text\": \"Kyiv\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyiv\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyiv\"}, {\"begin\": 2580, \"end\": 2587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso